  ('optometrist-moex-00437', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一患者的遠點為眼前20公分，若患者的屈光不正為軸性的屈光不正，眼球屈折力為+60.00DS，眼內折射 ° ° ° ° 率為1.333，則此患者眼軸長度為何？', '["20.51mm", "22.22mm", "24.24mm", "26.61mm"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00438', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一種方法為客觀性的測量散光？', '["鐘面圖", "Jackson交叉圓柱鏡", "視網膜檢影鏡（retinoscopy）", "裂孔板"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00439', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '以超音波儀測量眼球參數，超音波圖像估計從角膜後表面至晶體前表面的時間間隔為4.0 μS，以人體體溫 為37℃當作基礎條件，請問該眼球之前房深度為多少？（體溫37℃情況下，各介質的超音波穿透速率分 別是：角膜1,550m/s；房水1,532m/s；水晶體1,641m/s）', '["3.06mm", "3.25mm", "3.80mm", "4.16mm"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00440', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於角膜屈光力及屈光手術的關係，下列何者錯誤？', '["Radialkeratotomy（RK）手術是在角膜上做放射狀切口，導致角膜組織變平，從而降低眼睛的屈光力", "Laser-assistedinsitukeratomileusis（LASIK）手術中製作角膜瓣即可降低屈光力", "透過LASIK手術矯正遠視眼時，中心角膜會變陡而增加屈光力", "Photorefractivekeratectomy（PRK）手術使用準分子雷射雕刻角膜基質，亦可降低角膜的散光"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00441', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於眼球參數測量（包括眼介質弧度、厚度，眼球尺寸大小等）之方法，下列何者不適用？', '["光學儀器測量法（opticalmethods）", "超音波測量法（ultrasonography）", "X光測量法（X-ray）", "視覺誘發電位法（visualevokedpotential）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "68f98e0b0869", "answer_pdf_sha1": "6cdd7d434734", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0902", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
